flowchart TB
  A["developer request"]:::base --> B
  B["<b>Coding agent</b> (OpenCode / any MCP host) + <b>AGENTS.md</b> — the gate<br/><i>1 · sensitive signal? (intent / filename / schema keywords)</i>"]:::base --> C
