  D["<b>MCP tool&nbsp; log_decision(…)</b> &nbsp;→&nbsp; compliance-auditor (deterministic Python)<br/><i>3 · append-only</i>"]:::mcp --> E
  E["<b>audit-trail/decisions.jsonl</b> — SHA-256 hash chain<br/><i>seq N: { …, prev_hash, hash = sha256(canonical(record)) }</i>"]:::base
  E --> V["verify_audit_trail()<br/><i>recompute every link, localize tamper</i>"]:::out
  E --> R["generate_compliance_report()<br/><i>deterministic Model Card</i>"]:::out
  D -->|use case| U["<b>Child-safety chatbot</b><br/>a use case of the above<br/><i>grooming · bullying · abuse · self-harm · suicidal · distress</i>"]:::usecase

